OL,3,CChef delivers free Christmas dinners
OL,4,Cto more than 100 islanders
OL,6,FA Guernsey chef has spent 48 hours
OL,7,Fprepping Christmas roasts for more
OL,8,Fthan 100 islanders who can't make
OL,9,Fmeals for themselves.
OL,11,FMatt Bamford has spent the last two
OL,12,Fdays peeling, chopping, and roasting
OL,13,Fto provide islanders with a free
OL,14,Fdinner.
OL,16,FA small army of volunteers from every
OL,17,Fparish on the island assisted Matt in
OL,18,Fpreparing and delivering meals this
OL,19,FChristmas Eve.
