OL,3,CChef delivers free Christmas dinners
OL,4,Cto more than 100 islanders
OL,6,FThe meal includes a main course, a
OL,7,Fpudding, and a small present.
OL,9,FMatt said: "A lot of people have rung
OL,10,Fme and a lot of people got really
OL,11,Femotional. I think it's got me a bit
OL,12,Femotional as well, so it's good that
OL,13,Fit is.
OL,15,F"There's a lot of elderly people who
OL,16,Freached out and a couple of them come
OL,17,Finto the deli and they got teary that
OL,18,Fthe the husbands are in care and stuff
OL,19,Fon their own.
