OL,3,CChef delivers free Christmas dinners
OL,4,Cto more than 100 islanders
OL,6,F"That's the kind of people we wanted
OL,7,Fto reach out to."
OL,9,FMatt hopes that the meals will benefit
OL,10,Fpeople who struggle to get their own
OL,11,Fmeals, saying that no one should go
OL,12,Fwithout a Christmas meal.
OL,14,FVolunteer Scott Sarre explains: "We
OL,15,Fjust delivered to a gentleman clearly
OL,16,Funable to cook for himself.
OL,18,F"(Now) he doesn't have to worry about
OL,19,Fpreparing any food tomorrow. He (can)
OL,20,Fjust warm it through and has a
OL,21,FChristmas with a gift as well from us.
