OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F388A1735479571
OL,3,CChef delivers free Christmas dinners
OL,4,Cto more than 100 islanders
OL,6,F"It's quite shocking the amount of
OL,7,Fpeople who are on their own,
OL,8,Fespecially this time of year. It
OL,9,Fshouldn't be at any time, but this
OL,10,Ftime of year was even more sensitive.
OL,12,F"So if we were able to do just a
OL,13,Flittle bit just to give them something
OL,14,Fa little bit - a little bit of a
OL,15,Fsurprise on Christmas Day."
OL,17,FThis scheme - in its first year - has
OL,18,Falso been made possible by donations
OL,19,Ffrom local businesses.
