OL,4,Cto more than 100 islanders
OL,6,FDominic Buchette, who donated to the
OL,7,Fscheme, says: "We were impressed by
OL,8,F(Matt's) kindness making all this
OL,9,Feffort and working all over Christmas
OL,10,Fjust to support elderly, vulnerable
OL,11,Fpeople and people who need a nice
OL,12,Fboost at this time of year.
OL,14,F"It seemed like a worthy cause and it
OL,15,Fwas direct to the community, which is
OL,16,Fpretty much what we're all about."
